# {{ name }} Cloudflare Containers Deployment

This package publishes an admitted containerized artifact through a Worker-fronted Cloudflare
Containers target.

Keep `wrangler.jsonc` and `{{ cloudflare_worker_entrypoint_path }}` limited to provider-native
settings. Deployment identity, artifact admission, lane policy, ingress posture, and secret/runtime
requirements remain authoritative in `TARGETS`.

The container class, Durable Object binding, migration tag, and Worker entrypoint path are derived
from the deployment name and are not scaffold inputs.
